      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mb-4">Types, Uses, Advantages, and Specifications</p>
      <p class="text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mb-6">Alfa Laval industrial centrifuges are fluid separators designed and manufactured to separate fluids on a large scale. These centrifuges exert high centrifugal force to affect the separation of solids from liquids and liquids from liquids. From oil purifiers on marine vessels to coolant centrifuges in machining facilities, Alfa Laval industrial centrifuges are the global benchmark for reliable fluid separation. Dolphin Centrifuge stocks the complete line &mdash; new, rebuilt, and reconditioned &mdash; backed by decades of application expertise.</p>
